snippet.title: Hakan's War Manager - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Updated version of our gameplay trailer.
Hakan's War Manager is a fusion of ancient warfare and tactical strategy inspired by Football Manager. As the tactician of your clan, lead them to victory in a "War League", vying for the prestigious title of Hakan (Khan of Khans). Master the art of war!
Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2485980/Hakans_War_Manager/

#hakanswarmanager #indiegame #steam #videogame #simulationgames #strategygames
